headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid CDW and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since January 2025, CDW has been in a holding pattern, posting a small loss of 2.2% while floating around $177.36. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 5.3% gain during that period.
